      "span_text": "We match the life-history categories used by Hamrick et al. [CITATION_2] , who showed in a large meta-analysis that various life-history traits, including general plant type, range size, dispersal mechanism, pollination vector, breeding system and successional syndrome may influence genetic diversity."
